   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>	To my brother Eudaimon, Antiourios his brother, greeting. Leave me for the beans, to give to Paianos son of Petaous, twenty talents of silver, that is, 20 tal. only. And do not neglect this. 
</ab>
